### POST /api/v1/drivers/onboarding
### Descripción: Registro de conductor (vehículo). Requiere rol Driver o Admin.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (DriverOnboardingResponse) | 400 DRIVER_EXISTS, UNAUTHORIZED, etc.

# @name driverOnboarding
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/drivers/onboarding
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licenseNumber": "LIC123",
  "vehiclePlate": "ABC-1234",
  "vehicleModel": "Sedan",
  "vehicleColor": "Black"
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "driverId": "guid",
#   "isVerified": false
# }

### Response error (400):
# { "error": "string", "code": "DRIVER_EXISTS" | "UNAUTHORIZED" | ... }
